                    her to my parents house and she seamlessly bonded with everyone in my family to the extent that my mum invited her to her birthday party without 
                    my consent. 
                <br> </br>
                    Sept 22, 2021, she was officially introduced to my family and everyone loved her. The rest they say is history as this is the case 
                    of friendship metamorphosing into love. I look forward to a lifetime of love, joy and happiness with Grace and I promise to always treat her like
